{"tid":1789034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人撐住 唔可以比支那成功搞冧香港","createTime":"2019-12-19T07:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T07:41:20.000Z","uid":241832,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b048cc29c3fb638c535404f3f923eb10ea353ddd","tid":1789034,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"支那一路都話上海深圳可以取代香港<br />\n可能流浮山刀手到都未取代到<br />\n所以先不停搞香港<br />\n<br />\n香港人先係香港嘅核心價值<br />\n如果你放7百萬人落嚟<br />\n不出5年<br />\n上海深圳就取代到香港啦<br />\n因為都係你啲劣質人種"},{"pid":"826cceffff2b0d0701899fe7eeb5c516de4df208","tid":1789034,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"佢地根本就係覺得香港控制唔到<br />\n外國又要佢14億市場<br />\n所以不停搞鳩香港<br />\n搞死香港，佢以為外資就一定要係大陸設總部<br />\n因為要佢14億人口市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4942f81564b794424eecc180eb66b72c890fa599","tid":1789034,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEmKLcT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDEmKLcT.jpg&h=de99bab4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"459917563e069568ad0ebfc67825bb843f8b5c1c","tid":1789034,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfG5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=16538607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F